*+
*  Name:
*     AST_PKG_CMN

*  Purpose:
*     Define logical array holding loaded status of ASTERIX sub-packages

*  Language:
*     Starlink Fortran

*  Type of Module:
*     Global variables include file.

*  Description:
*     This files defines a logical variable for each allowed ASTERIX sub
*     package number.

*  Prior Requirements:
*     None.

*  References:
*     FCI Subroutine Guide : http://www.sr.bham.ac.uk/asterix-docs/Programmer/Guides/fci.html

*  Keywords:
*     package:fci, usage:public

*  Authors:
*     DJA: David J. Allan (Jet-X, University of Birmingham)
*     {enter_new_authors_here}

*  History:
*     7 Mar 1996 (DJA):
*        Original version.
*     {enter_changes_here}

*-

*  Global Variables:
      LOGICAL			AST__LPACK(AST__MXPKG)

*  Integer aligned values
      COMMON /AST_PKG_CMN/   	AST__LPACK

*  Save common block contents
      SAVE /AST_PKG_CMN/
*.
